{"tid":1257911,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那：加拿大偽造獸醫衞生證書，將停止進口肉類產品","createTime":"2019-06-25T23:10:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T00:33:11.000Z","uid":42188,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"867d101ab7e5893588f23780217ba4b74f6cc01b","tid":1257911,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T23:10:16.000Z","msg":"加拿大傳媒周二報道，中國將於周三起停止進口加拿大肉類產品。<br />\n<br />\n《蒙特利爾周刊》（Le Journal de Montreal）引述中國駐蒙特利爾總領事館一名官員，指中國封殺加拿大肉類產品，因中方在來自加拿大的肉類產品中，發現偽造獸醫衞生證書，顯示加方監管不足。<br />\n<br />\n中加兩國去年12月因華為副董事長孟晚舟在溫哥華被捕事件而關係惡化。中方對加拿大農產品出口商諸多刁難，兩大芥花籽出口商4月遭中國以「有蟲害」為由取消註冊後，加拿大的大豆、豬肉等農產品也在出口中國時遇阻滯。<br />\n<br />\n路透社本月初報道，加拿大駐華大使館接到中方通知，中國海關當局計劃加強檢查從加拿大進口肉類及肉類製品，將開貨櫃甚至對所有肉類產品檢查。"},{"pid":"b2b371d4474174adf6d37adac87e2beb007277c7","tid":1257911,"uid":192052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T23:21:24.000Z","msg":"Link？"},{"pid":"1f3951eb0b55ee7c56f980f276a2026f9da59d2e","tid":1257911,"uid":40356,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T23:23:32.000Z","msg":"Source?"},{"pid":"e145f1482d60650c8f45c3f956c44e00a588a351","tid":1257911,"uid":123969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T23:26:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ca.reuters.com/article/idUSKCN1TQ2UZ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fca.reuters.com%2Farticle%2FidUSKCN1TQ2UZ&d=hgakeblNVNpTjPSl%2FdBGDo5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=e5b1d17e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fca.reuters.com%2Farticle%2FidUSKCN1TQ2UZ&h=5a0a0d5a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ca.reuters.com/article/idUSKCN1TQ2UZ</a>"},{"pid":"807b9543175093806170104e0f831a346560095f","tid":1257911,"uid":53466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T23:29:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a83815f40ed660d1eceaa48701e620ce204cc64b","tid":1257911,"uid":70183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T23:29:49.000Z","msg":"支那仲有肉食咩"